rComments: Professor Mcleod-Kilmurray is an excellent expert in this area, and she is very considerate for students. The class was of very high quality. We had a lot of great guess speakers, many are leading experts. The content of the class materials were well prepared and organized, and the lectures and discussions of high value and inspiring.

Overall a very good professor. Walk you through at least 2 mid-term and final practice exams. Final involves many parties and issues, so be aware of your time. Speaks a bit fast but very clear, also gives good homework feedback, but doesn't give out "A"s that often.
